description:
Fixed a few wrong notes in the bass part.

During the verse there are 2 bars where Tim ends the bars on a D/E respectively... the original tab started those bars on a B: those bars clearly start on an A! (the 5th up from B).

During the last bar of the bridge, the original tab only had the bass playing a D... it's a D / E 4 times.

Before the big ending, Tim plays D B D B... The last B is an octave up. Fixed.
title: Gasoline
